#: ../workspaces/workspace_tasks/index.rst:8
msgid "In a workspace in Quaive you can use tasks to define small pieces of work and - if you want - assign this to another user. Tasks can be closed when the job is finished and reopened again if this seems necessary. A notification email is sent out to the different users when a task was edited or it's status was changed."
msgstr ""

